    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, complete with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has been maintained with an eye toward performance, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry that preserves the communicative hydraulic steering feel. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved performance machine, the mechanical vitals remain stout, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul and valve adjustment, ensuring this M-car is ready for the technical curves of a backroad.",
